    Dialogues:
    - PlayerIsSpeaker: 0
      VoiceSpeaker: 1
      Dialogue: Every 100 years, the stars shower the Earth.
    - PlayerIsSpeaker: 0
      VoiceSpeaker: 1
      Dialogue: While beautiful, this phenomenon is deadly. However, from that destruction,
        a new magical landscape is born, flourishing despite its trauma and rebuilding
        itself into something fantastical.
    - PlayerIsSpeaker: 0
      VoiceSpeaker: 1
      Dialogue: The village of Alora is built upon those remains.
    - PlayerIsSpeaker: 0
      VoiceSpeaker: 1
      Dialogue: But, after years of thriving, Alora was awoken one night by bright
        lights in the sky. The land was once again overcome by a cosmic meltdown.
    - PlayerIsSpeaker: 0
      VoiceSpeaker: 1
      Dialogue: "Villagers exposed to the stardust were soon corrupted, overwhelmed
        by the stars\u2019 magical energy, forgetting their past selves."
    - PlayerIsSpeaker: 0
      VoiceSpeaker: 1
      Dialogue: One individual was completely crushed by a falling star, and their
        soul was released into the Earth. It wandered free, but its lonely journey
        was short lived.
    - PlayerIsSpeaker: 0
      VoiceSpeaker: 1
      Dialogue: It soon found a small robot. The soul breathed life into this small
        droid, and using what strength remained in the robot, every gear turning,
        they emerged from the ground.
    - PlayerIsSpeaker: 0
      VoiceSpeaker: 1
      Dialogue: "Their name is Loid. They have no memory of the person they once
        were, but they feel some kind of attachment to the people of the village.
        They all must be saved, though Loid doesn\u2019t know why."
    - PlayerIsSpeaker: 0
      VoiceSpeaker: 1
      Dialogue: Each individual must be cured by a unique elixir, which Loid can
        make by gathering ingredients around the village. One herb and one item of
        personal value should do the trick.
    - PlayerIsSpeaker: 0
      VoiceSpeaker: 1
      Dialogue: Pay attention to what each person needs. Free them from cosmic corruption
        by bringing them a concoction of what they most desire.
